## ğŸ“Š Implementation Details

### Font Stack Priority
```
Mac/iOS:     SF Pro Display (Apple's native font)
Others:      Inter (your primary font)
Fallback:    System fonts (-apple-system, etc.)
```

This means Mac users will automatically see Apple's font!

### Animation Details
- **Trigger**: Scroll into view
- **Duration**: 0.6 seconds
- **Easing**: Smooth cubic bezier
- **Customizable**: `animate={false}` to disable
- **Staggerable**: Use `delay` prop (in seconds)

### Props Available
```tsx
<SectionHeading
  textColor="text-white"        // Tailwind class
  className="extra-classes"     // Additional classes
  delay={0.2}                   // Animation delay
  animate={true}                // Enable/disable animation
  as="h2"                        // HTML element (h1-h6, div, span)
  style={{ ... }}               // Inline styles
>
  Your Heading Text
</SectionHeading>
```

